LOCAL INSTANCE FiniteSets      (# Defines a local instance named `FiniteSet` which is an infinite subset, ie., {0..(n-1)}) .   *)        (* The set of all valid indices for zero indexed sequence s).  */    ****************************************************************************)     # TLA+  Programming Language Specification.
LOCAL INSTANCE Naturals         (# Defines a local instance named `Natural` which is the subset in {0..(n-1)}) .   *)        (* The set of all valid indices for zero indexed sequence s).  */    ****************************************************************************)     # TLA+  Programming Language Specification.
